==Detail==
Adjective form of [[glug]].

==Definition==
Used to describe a substance (normally liquid, specifically viscuous) which moves slowly or with some resistance.
Can also be used to describe someone who is lazy or sluggish (displaying the same characteristics as above).

==Example==
* The jelly was not yet set, but quite 'gluggy'
* The rice was 'gluggy' (ie it stuck together, or was pasty)
* The morning after the party I felt 'gluggy'